       </p>

      </div>
      <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA09d365n1-ptr" id="PJA09d365n1">1</a>
       
   <p><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Cool Thoughts</span>, p. 4647.</p>

      </div>
      <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA09d365n2-ptr" id="PJA09d365n2">2</a>
       
   <p>Or <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">ceteris paribus</span>, that is, other things being equal.</p>

